  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK650">
<l>iṇarūḻttum nāṟām alaraṉaiyar kaṟṟa </l>
<l>tuṇara viritturaiyā tār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are unable to set forth their acquirements (before others) are like flowers blossoming in a cluster and yet without fragrance.</l>
